name: "DO YOUR OWN THING" - Crest Tee - White
description:
The inspiration and vision of this collection comes from the cult classic film, "Do The Right Thing". "Do The Right Thing" depicts the racial tension within the diverse neighborhood of Brooklyn, NY. The story revolves around the main character, "Mookie" and his close group of friends. As for Mookee By Yuske, we too are a collective group of diverse individuals. We come together as a group that unite around style and culture. 

This is "Do Your Own Thing"
